## 9. Template: Pergunta — SEO Estruturado (`templates/community/question.html`)

### Schema.org QAPage (máximo SEO para perguntas):

```html
{% block extra_head %}
<link rel="canonical" href="https://SEUDOMINIO.com.br/comunidade/{{ question.category.slug }}/{{ question.slug }}/">

<!-- Schema.org QAPage -->
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "QAPage",
  "mainEntity": {
    "@type": "Question",
    "name": "{{ question.title|escapejs }}",
    "text": "{{ question.body|escapejs }}",
    "dateCreated": "{{ question.created_at|date:'Y-m-d' }}",
    "author": {"@type": "Person", "name": "{{ question.author_name|escapejs }}"},
